<div>
     <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    <p>
    <p><strong>Company Overview</strong></p>
    <p><strong>Hello World Petshop</strong> is your one-stop destination for all things pets. Founded with a deep love for animals and a commitment to excellent service, our pet shop has been serving the community since 2010. Our goal is to make every pet&#39;s life a bit brighter and every pet owner&#39;s experience a bit easier.</p>
    <p><strong>Our Story</strong></p>
    <p>The idea for Hello World Petshop came from a shared passion among friends who wanted to create a pet store that felt more like a community hub than a typical retail experience. We envisioned a place where pet lovers could find everything they need while feeling supported and informed by a team that truly understands the joys and challenges of pet ownership.</p>
    <p><strong>Our Values</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <p><strong>Commitment to Quality</strong>: We believe in offering only the best for your pets. Our products are carefully selected to ensure they meet the highest standards of safety and quality.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p><strong>Customer-Centric Approach</strong>: Your satisfaction is our top priority. We take the time to understand your needs and offer personalized service that makes shopping for your pets a pleasure.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p><strong>Community Engagement</strong>: We’re not just about selling products; we’re about making a difference. We actively support local shelters and rescue organizations, and we host events and workshops to promote pet welfare and education.</p>
        </li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>What We Offer</strong></p>
    <p>At Hello World Petshop, we offer a wide range of products and services designed to cater to pets of all kinds. Our store features:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <p><strong>Premium Pet Food</strong>: A diverse selection of high-quality food options to keep your pets healthy and happy, including brands like Nutro, Blue Buffalo, and Royal Canin.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p><strong>Toys and Accessories</strong>: Engaging toys and stylish accessories that cater to the needs and preferences of pets and their owners, from KONG chew toys to personalized pet collars.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p><strong>Grooming Supplies</strong>: Products to keep your pets looking their best, from shampoos and conditioners by Earthbath to grooming tools like Furminators and nail clippers.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p><strong>Comfort and Care</strong>: Bedding, carriers, and other essentials that ensure your pets are comfortable and well cared for, including plush beds, cozy blankets, and travel carriers.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <p><strong>Expert Advice</strong>: Our knowledgeable staff is always on hand to provide advice and answer your questions about pet care, training, and health.</p>
        </li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Our Team</strong></p>
    <p>Our team at Hello World Petshop is made up of dedicated pet enthusiasts who bring a wealth of experience and a genuine love for animals to the job. From our friendly sales associates to our knowledgeable pet care advisors, each member of our team is committed to helping you and your pets live your best lives.</p>
    <p><strong>Connect With Us</strong></p>
    <p>Stay updated with the latest news, special offers, and pet care tips by following us on social media and subscribing to our newsletter. We’re excited to be part of your pet’s journey and look forward to seeing you at Hello World Petshop!</p>
    <p><strong>Contact Us</strong></p>
    <p>For more information about our products and services, or if you have any questions, please feel free to reach out to us:</p>
