        <li><strong>Phone</strong>: (555) 123-4567</li>
        <li><strong>Email</strong>: info@helloworldpetshop.com</li>
        <li><strong>Address</strong>: 123 Pet Avenue, Pawsburg, CA 90210</li>
        <li><strong>Website</strong>: <a href="http://www.helloworldpetshop.com">www.helloworldpetshop.com</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p>Thank you for choosing Hello World Petshop – where every pet is part of our world!</p>

    </p>
